      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial CFD solver with documented QA procedures and version control meets MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 is used under a validated QA framework. Release notes, regression test suite, and configuration management records are available. Version-controlled case files and run scripts are archived in the project repository. MRL 2 requirement of level 2 is satisfied."
    },
    {
