      "rationale": "All simulations achieved residual convergence to 1e-6 for continuity and momentum equations. Mass imbalance was below 0.005% in all cases. Iterative solver error is negligible relative to discretization uncertainty."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
